Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,真是久違的任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,鳴人 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,也不是什麼值得興奮的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,與火之國接壤的邊境小國的小村莊發生了慘案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說那裏的居民慘遭滅門
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亙古以來 那裏就被視為聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱巨坑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言那裏藏有秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打擊覬覦秘寶的盜賊們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏防守嚴密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍覆沒也太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖想盡可能增派人手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但村裏如今也不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前日發生的村外臨時墓地被破壞事件嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且封印著曉成員的森林裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那起鐮刀被盜事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我們要忙上一陣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能無視平民們的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖出襲擊村子的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予其應得的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上都燒成灰燼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙是用什麼武器襲擊村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀的樹林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面明明是寸草不生的荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏應該是寶庫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的泉水應該通往某處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下竟有如此的空間…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.93,0:03:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想趁火打劫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是受命而來的木葉忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來調查這座村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是守護附近八丁鎮的警衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和托尼卡村交好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人向你引見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些貴客是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你們如此迅速前來支援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫迪索納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是八丁鎮的鎮長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前日那些倖免於難的村民們前來求助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得知了此事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任何入侵者的線索嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的守衛和覬覦秘寶的盜賊們有過多次衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道那個寶物到底是什麼嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕村裏瞭解真相的也不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說根本不知道是誰為了什麼而襲擊這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的水真甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這巨坑簡直就像在吸收周圍的活力和生息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謳歌著繁榮一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的泉水充滿著生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那麼愛打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這附近想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在做一些研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:07:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些蛇是我用大蛇丸大人的細胞製成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧其強大的再生力 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈指間便能大量繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 借助我偉大的實驗成果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以移植其他生物的細胞核
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重現遺傳資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧合的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的水能夠迅速促進細胞分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和病毒不相上下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 重生…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是曉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 飛段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你出現在這裏不是偶然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊村子的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好給我解釋解釋 說說經過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓得到…我嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不會讓你逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋子並非就此一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是…曉的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯瑪老師和疾風老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…穢土轉生 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你盜的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來會很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道忍術的火候還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 千萬別被對方碰到血液
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 快無法呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜很喜歡這個旋律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自己編的嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到的 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒畫完呢 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊 過來拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多克老師嗎 他還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又胖了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就像熊先生一樣 很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟啪啪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肥嘟嘟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來比起守衛 他更適合當老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 我不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 誰來救救我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐 雷歐 雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多克老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跳下來 我會接住的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿出勇氣來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力哦 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你了 雷歐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裏也許還有其他人需要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜不想見小義和小紗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒回來就去八丁鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那裏後向官府求助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,上古之神創造的天之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,被污穢之人奪去了力量
